      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This car is ready for a transformation! While it's currently in poor condition and needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for any enthusiast or mechanic looking to bring a vehicle back to life. Grab this opportunity to build your dream car from the ground up!",
